{
  "stem": "717.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't remember how long we-- couldn't have been very long.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In the same building, in the same house where I used to go to school before the war-- it wasn't very far from where we lived.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Used to walk there all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] When the announcement came that we had to leave town, we had to leave our apartments, the only place we could go was to my maternal grandparents, because they lived in Baluty.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So apparently, it was decided between them that we're going to move in with them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Things weren't very comfortable.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They had a larger apartment than ours.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Also one huge room which was divided.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that's where they put-- in fact, there was another gentleman there after we moved in that my grandfather used to work for, the owner of that company, the factory where they printed the materials.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He had a tiny, little beard, a white beard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He must have been a very rich man before the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he stayed with them because he had nowhere else to stay.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He was kicked out of his apartment in town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I remember the trip.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We rented the horse and little wagon so we can put all our belongings.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I remember the Germans filming it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I remember the soldiers standing there in the brown uniforms, the NSKK-- what was the [NON-ENGLISH], something-- with cameras, with movie cameras, filming it while we were going.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I was sitting high there on top of all the-- our furniture, whatever we could, we were allowed to take.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I don't remember that we, we were allowed to take everything or some parts of it.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
